&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate will have a strong and diverse background with an emphasis on software development for embedded systems.&amp;nbsp; Prior experience working on multi-disciplinary projects that exist at the confluence of mechanical, electrical, systems, and software engineering is strongly desired.&amp;nbsp; Finally, the ideal candidate should be able to decompose complex problems into their constituent components, devise plans for executing each piece of the problem, and follow-through on solution development, test, and verification.&lt;/p&gt;
